   MINOR-COLUMN _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ About a month ago, I read
an article in a money magazine about family finances. According to
them, the most important thing in a couple's life is not great sex
or simpatico political views or how easily you talk over your
frozen Stouffer's dinner. The No. 1 component for happy married
