<P>
   VIDEO-RINGEL _ Coinciding with the 40th anniversary of Francois
Truffaut's ``The 400 Blows,'' Fox Lorber Cinema has released six of
the great director's classic films on video and DVD. In addition to
the Cannes Film Festival winner ``The 400 Blows,'' the titles
include ``Shoot the Piano Player,'' ``The Last Metro,''
``Confidentially Yours,'' ``Love on the Run'' and ``Two English
Girls.'' (Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   AUDIO-POP _ Review of new disc from techno pioneer MOBY.
(Hamilton, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   AUDIO-MINIS _ Short reviews of albums by Blaque, Tim McGraw and
C- Note. (Staff, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   AUDIO-COUNTRY _ A review of country artist Tim McGraw's latest
CD, which is doing quite well on the charts. (MLongino, Atlanta
journal-Constitution). 10.
