</P>
<P>
   HKN-THRASH _ The expansion draft is less than a month away and
the Atlanta Thrashers still don't have a coach. Why is general
manager Don Waddell waiting so long and who are the candidates? For
the first time, Waddell admits a coach may not be named before the
draft. (Schultz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
