   TV-RATINGS _ WASHINGTON _ Sen. Joseph Lieberman, D-Conn., and
Sen. Sam Brownback, R-Kan., join the Parents Television Council at
a news conference to release a new study titled, ``Unintended
Consequences: With Rating System in Place, TV More Offensive Than
