   SOCIAL-SECURITY _ WASHINGTON _ The House votes Wednesday on
``lock box'' legislation that would prevent money in the Social
Security trust fund from being spent for any other purpose. The
bill, opposed by Democrats, gives the GOP a rare chance to gain
political advantage on the Social Security issue. (Lipman, Cox News
Service).
